{"type":"message","id":"5faf9b6f","parentId":"c00ead93","timestamp":"2026-04-05T03:07:52.106Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dkbxjsf8c2om_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- Fetching skill\nstock-daily-analysis  Stock Daily Analysis\nSummary: LLM驱动的每日股票分析系统。支持A股/港股/美股自选股智能分析，生成决策仪表盘和大盘复盘报告。提供技术面分析（均线、MACD、RSI、乖离率）、趋势判断、买入信号评分。可与market-data skill集成获取更稳定的ETF数据。触发词：股票分析、分析股票、每日分析、技术面分析。\nOwner: robottk\nCreated: 2026-03-15T04:26:59.386Z\nUpdated: 2026-04-04T06:46:10.189Z\nLatest: 1.0.0\nTags: latest=1.0.0\nSelected: 1.0.0\nSelected At: 2026-03-15T04:26:59.386Z\nChangelog: Initial release\nFiles:\nOPEN_SOURCE_REVIEW.md  4.8KB  f7bd9459aaad100b7d29db2e259c6e96da2424a81f0e8c9e46b2617e33e2c906  text/markdown\nREADME.md  5.3KB  70ce357a6f5f78d35a7998fec14ed82d30ff3ad4c18e2357b3b2069569c46625  text/markdown\nSKILL.md  2.4KB  8240f825afc434760139ccdae334b67c416e93346c94663303457999ce36006b  text/markdown\nconfig.example.json  553B  c52d82d6dd7cf7b5844cfb76e738de5fcbbcd8198d108fa91194faa0a247645a  application/json\nrequirements.txt  95B  36aa125012f81a8b2f0321dac7d5b24171a604172265016099e754d4b6f4f787  text/plain\nscripts/ai_analyzer.py  7.6KB  8c5de988c7564c3f54787866fc7f606a6939bf133a4f23519bafa423d42801b5  text/plain\nscripts/analyzer.py  4.5KB  a1332e4be86fc0a731e6c2f03e9d2840d7e88d54d9805330f6b847250a23e2a0  text/plain\nscripts/data_fetcher.py  11KB  21d8c24b4771e113d2287454ba493dae818312ee0132e5c781caaa3c893a7b9c  text/plain\nscripts/market_data_bridge.py  6.6KB  b96824d58855957cfa02435407347b47b4bb69343f3ccd472d68d03f0025b30f  text/plain\nscripts/notifier.py  6.6KB  4fad7bcf48702e49fec6b500798db04176d5fdf092cbfd00a83b96c326fac413  text/plain\nscripts/run.sh  824B  a690382ffd59475bb8169a0224b7b5aa4af446e0fe4fc2c03014aa408b5d7c06  application/x-sh\nscripts/setup.sh  1.2KB  23048e782b1f0b948a5f4b761290fc869cbd07bb042362ef24ad6fa5a3560c38  application/x-sh\nscripts/trend_analyzer.py  22KB  a70f26d03ae15690761cbd96d44b527b438