{"type":"message","id":"056321f8","parentId":"7f7e0067","timestamp":"2026-04-05T03:09:15.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All the shared files (ai_analyzer.py, data_fetcher.py, trend_analyzer.py, analyzer.py) are identical between the local repo and the clawhub skill. The clawhub skill is essentially a subset of the local repo (just with a different SKILL.md wrapper).\n\nSo the situation is:\n- The clawhub skill `stock-daily-analysis` is a packaged version of the same underlying project\n- The local repo has all the same scripts as the clawhub skill (and more)\n- The only difference is the SKILL.md format\n\nThe user's request \"daily_stock_analysis将更新与本地仓库合并\" has been fulfilled - the GitHub origin/main updates have been merged. The clawhub skill doesn't have additional updates beyond what the GitHub repo already has (since the GitHub repo is the source).\n\n\nThe SKILL.md files differ structurally, but they describe the same functionality, so there's nothing substantive to merge from the clawhub version. I should summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"5eeef2c88d9a1418fb7c9b0e589c3a5092ae93cfa36987d64eb169c54552034a"},{"type":"text","text":"Clawhub skill 的核心脚本（`analyzer.py`、`ai_analyzer.py`、`data_fetcher.py`、`trend_analyzer.py`）与本地仓库完全一致，没有差异需要合并。\n\n**合并结果：**\n\n✅ GitHub `origin/main` 已 Fast-forward 合并到本地，100个文件，+7919行变更，主要更新包括：\n- 新增 `longbridge_fetcher.py`（港股数据）\n- `data_provider/base.py` 重构\n- `src/agent/` 多项增强（llm_adapter、orchestrator、runner）\n- `src/services/system_config_service.py` 大幅扩充\n- 新增多个测试文件\n- 文档更新（CHANGELOG、FAQ、DEPLOY等）\n\nClawhub skill 是本地仓库的子集，无额外更新。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16258,"output":370,"cacheRead":21619,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38247,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775358545703,"responseId":"06210554aaa6ad58eab7aa25a094ddc0"}}
